Takeda Sales in China May Reach $1 Billion in 4 to 5 Years

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-09-16T02:41:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/takeda-sales-in-china-may-reach-1-billion-in-4-to-5-years.html
Takeda Pharmaceutical Co.’s sales
in  China  may reach $1 billion in four to five years, Vice
President Haruhiko Hirate said in an interview today.  The company plans to invest $300 million in China over the
next 36 months, Hirate said in the Chinese city of Dalian, where
he’s attending the World Economic Forum meetings.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  